cmail
=====

A very simple email client.

usage: cmail.py [-h] [-u USERNAME] [-p PASSWORD] [-s SMTP] [-sp PORT] -f FROM -t TO [-re SUBJECT]

Send electronic mail

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -u USERNAME, --username USERNAME
                        Server login username. Default env var 'CMAIL_USERNAME'.
  -p PASSWORD, --password PASSWORD
                        Server login password. Default env var 'CMAIL_PASSWORD'.
  -s SMTP, --smtp SMTP  Server smtp address. Default env 'CMAIL_SMTP'.
  -sp PORT, --port PORT
                        Server port. Default env 'CMAIL_SMTP_PORT'.
  -f FROM, --from FROM  From address
  -t TO, --to TO        Recipient address
  -re SUBJECT, --subject SUBJECT
                        Email subject. Default date.
